{"tid":2145093,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"胡鍚進代表中共笠水：「中國哪一步反制　哪一步藐視需智慧」","createTime":"2020-08-08T01:10:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-08T02:13:07.000Z","uid":149494,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c5e40c5e3576c5f4579613a050472363cc145aed","tid":2145093,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:10:22.000Z","msg":"內地環球時報總編輯胡錫進批評，美國宣布制裁行政長官林鄭月娥等11名香港與內地官員及前官員，是十分無恥的長臂管轄，以及赤裸裸地干涉中國內政。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進相信，名單上的人都對美國這招早有思想準備，制裁對內地官員不會有什麼影響，而林鄭月娥亦曾經表示，無資產在美國，不給簽證就不去美國。<br />\n<br />\n胡錫進說，美國一日內推出兩項針對中國的措施是太瘋狂，認為特朗普團隊的對華政治激進思維，被他們選情不利形勢逼到沸騰，反問世界上何時見過這樣無厘頭的大國博弈。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">胡錫進認為，中國應該反制時必須反制，但看來不能夠每次都去陪華盛頓玩，因為對方明顯發癲，中方總不能夠與他們一樣癲，哪一步應該反制，哪一步藐視，需要智慧。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n他又估計，美國未來三個月還會出更多牌，特朗普團隊故意找中國的茬，刻意令中美關係升溫，目的就是為了勝選連任，雖然很多西方民眾對中國有偏見，但他們都意識到美國變得瘋狂，中國保持理性。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542511-20200808.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542511-20200808.htm&d=973ie4zpYy9ax4bL%2F%2BCgDJuyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=585f4bc7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542511-20200808.htm&h=52b67fdf\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542511-20200808.htm</a>"},{"pid":"58fb3f906bd15b8ac7df364306d25615b2573bd9","tid":2145093,"uid":51271,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:16:35.000Z","msg":"美中和好，反中撚炒哂車#3 -- 回憶小子<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1891475\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1891475</a>"},{"pid":"01d6597bf5941f2cdc40c83298dd83d38f35c3ba","tid":2145093,"uid":230639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:30:19.000Z","msg":"比人禁住打仲係到嘈 笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6dda98ecbcb04f30a43503cbdd896b800bac953","tid":2145093,"uid":7169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"即係用對眼掘住美國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5aa66c8dc08eb92cbde0ee95b14bbd222d5da813","tid":2145093,"uid":160502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:33:19.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"xx-large\">我國又贏</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span class=\"small\"><strong><span class=\"navy\">媽呀！ 好柒啊！</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f0ab5cf545438255351713302053e3bfc264330","tid":2145093,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f6dda98ecbcb04f30a43503cbdd896b800bac953","tid":2145093,"uid":7169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:32:12.000Z","msg":"即係用對眼掘住美國人？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yeah.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3igPRF1.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3igPRF1.gif&h=1fc7a3f1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"535cf5aa3d99036cffca245e477f4db861487a88","tid":2145093,"uid":322642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WFDOnNV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWFDOnNV.jpg&h=36f2ec42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/irxb41f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Firxb41f.jpg&h=c9b58a62&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e1d5b46a939b3b2ee276e989d6e6863eaee2ac25","tid":2145093,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:36:51.000Z","msg":"想當年我仲讀緊BAND 3中學<br />\n有條MK撚狗咁撚我, 話約我隻揪<br />\n佢以為自己有腹肌就好撚好打<br />\n(但其實我當時己經舉左兩三年鐵,一直有飲奶粉<br />\n不過我BULK緊, 即係夜神起義 Bane 果種大隻型<br />\n所以D肌肉線條未現到出黎)<br />\n我D 毒撚FD 嚇撚到標尿<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「唔好同佢打呀, 佢有腹肌架」<br />\n「你痴左線咩, 你見唔見到佢幾咁FIT 呀」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我心諗話你怕你嬲<br />\n有腹肌唔等於有力量<br />\n我笑笑口咁答應左條MK 放學去籃球場打過<br />\nfast forward 去到決戰時間<br />\n成班同學企哂係側邊睇<br />\n佢就除左件校服<br />\n成個小丑咁係到谷佢果幾舊腹肌仔<br />\n<br />\n見到成班以為佢好好打果個情景,我真係快忍不住笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然最後佢打到我仆街, 牙都甩埋<br />\n但完全同腹肌冇關"},{"pid":"55a5feee600762924d23d176555e9055c37899ad","tid":2145093,"uid":47176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:39:01.000Z","msg":"姐係之前唔智慧?"},{"pid":"bcc15ddd6e80e8807d4ab2941471de0017ac5116","tid":2145093,"uid":130797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T01:39:42.000Z","msg":"哎呀<br />\n支那大洪水都只係上帝發癲<br />\n所以北京先無配合黎玩玩<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92ecf63900439b201c4425389f89687ffd7b6e28","tid":2145093,"uid":215876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:05:20.000Z","msg":"五毛小子<br />\n你阿頭叫你話佢地笠水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"6b34b9215af6d8b26087b3addea589478005a8b8","tid":2145093,"uid":83206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-08T02:13:07.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">反中撚炒左車未呀柒頭支那賤畜五毛回憶小子？<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n中美和好，反中撚炒哂車<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/886259\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/886259</a>"}]}